{"tid":1170225,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿前妻搶屋後想趕走他　男索性炸屋圖同歸於盡","createTime":"2019-05-25T01:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T07:44:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e5d61a580a04e30e6de44bc6daf2f3fe10f3809","tid":1170225,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:07:51.000Z","msg":"英國多塞特郡（Dorset）一名68歲的男子，因為不滿63歲的前妻「搶走」房子，索性把房子引爆、破壞。但因爆炸時，兩人都在屋內，爆炸也差點奪去他們性命。男子周三（22日）被判刑5年4個月。<br />\n克洛斯（Ian Clowes）於2015年與老婆伊萊恩（Elaine Clowes）離婚，兩人把位於多塞特郡普爾（Poole）的半獨立式住宅拆成兩部分。後來克洛斯遇上嚴重的財政困難，伊萊恩獲法庭批准，獲得房子的所有權，並向克洛斯支付6.5萬英鎊（約260.12萬元台幣）。<br />\n伊萊恩後來計劃賣掉房子的上層部分，但她會留在下層居住，克洛斯不滿意這樣的安排，於是把兩個氣瓶帶進屋內，密謀炸屋。伊萊恩於去年10月22日聽到住宅上層有噪音，然後天花板就塌了下來，瓦礫將她埋住。身處上層的克洛斯全身也有30%燒傷，送醫後要人工昏迷治療，並住院至今年1月。<br />\n克洛斯早前承認縱火罪，周三被判囚5年4個月，且須向伊萊恩及鄰居賠償，賠償金額待定。法官富勒（Jonathan Fuller）形容克洛斯的行動「邪惡」，對前妻造成重大傷害，「這罪行出自一定程度的惡意，你不希望你妻子得到你買下的房子。這是邪惡的，對她造成沉重的心理負擔。」<br />\n庭上讀出伊萊恩的聲明，指「她從未想過克洛斯會有報復的想法」，「近年他對我的關注不多，但我絕不認為他會做出這樣的事，我在情感上有很大壓力。」（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190525/640_79ce366a4cc84243b0ea8aad7909fe5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190525%2F640_79ce366a4cc84243b0ea8aad7909fe5c.jpg&h=a3b070cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190525/640_70eedbed0d391d5f53177a7dfd714deb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190525%2F640_70eedbed0d391d5f53177a7dfd714deb.jpg&h=f64098c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190525/640_fe05e4563809b4d600244fb0d0c20ee2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190525%2F640_fe05e4563809b4d600244fb0d0c20ee2.jpg&h=f2027faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190525/640_735a44c547eb1feaa59c872c536a6d64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190525%2F640_735a44c547eb1feaa59c872c536a6d64.jpg&h=3225cbd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190525/640_1cd7f6319b584104bea3999302511c1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190525%2F640_1cd7f6319b584104bea3999302511c1c.jpg&h=d9d92fe2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66eee96e45dd8eec8b68129bda1389b73e96198f","tid":1170225,"uid":249885,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:28:13.000Z","msg":"同支那婆結婚嘅廢老可以學下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd518eeed216b958eb5f79748d478b967120b47b","tid":1170225,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:29:56.000Z","msg":"蝧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7146f721499b628dc3d0936a9d32fa742a6ca5","tid":1170225,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66eee96e45dd8eec8b68129bda1389b73e96198f","tid":1170225,"uid":249885,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:28:13.000Z","msg":"同支那婆結婚嘅廢老可以學下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}